               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>This manuscript of the <title xml:lang="sa">Bṛhaspatismṛti</title> is the fourth in a collection of five <term xml:lang="sa">smṛti</term> texts. This text is a short treatise on <term xml:lang="sa">dāna</term>, not to be confused with the ancient <title xml:lang="sa">Bṛhaspatismṛti</title> which survives only in quotations.</p>
<p>Although the text transmitted here is similiar to the one given in printed editions, it differs significantly, and the end is completely different.</p>
</summary>
                  
               <msItem defective="true"><title xml:lang="sa">Bṛhaspatismṛti</title><textLang mainLang="san"/><incipit xml:lang="sa"><milestone n="1r" facs="125" unit="folio"/>
<lb n="1"/>iṣṭvā sarvvakratun rājā samāptaparidakṣiṇaḥ
maghavān vibudhaśreṣṭhaḥ paryyapṛcchat_ bṛhaspatiṃ -

bhagavan_ kena dānena svargatas sukham edhate |
yad akṣayaṃ mahābhā<lb n="2"/>ga tat brūhi vadatāṃ vara -

evaṃ pṛṣṭas sa indreṇa devadeva purohitaḥ
vācaspatir mmahātejo bṛhaspatir uvāca ha |

hiraṇyadānaṃ godānaṃ bhumidānan ca <lb n="3"/>vāsava -
etat_ prayacchamāno hi svargadas sukham edhate |

sūvarṇaṃ rajataṃ vastraṃ maṇiratnaṃ vasūri ca -
<unclear>sarvva</unclear>m etat_ bhaved dattaṃ vasudhāṃ yaḥ prayacchati |

<lb n="4"/>phalakṛṣṭān mahīn dadyāt_ sabījāṃ sasya<unclear>śā</unclear>linīṃ |
yāvat sūryyakarā loke tāvat svarge mahīyyate -

yac cāpi kurute pāvaṃ puruṣo vṛttikarśitaḥ -
<lb n="5"/>api gokarṇamātreṇa bhumidānena śudhyati -

saptahastena vāsam yat_ triṃśaddaṇḍe<del>na</del> pi varddhanaṃ -
sa śatāsv ekagokarṇṇaṃ iti vedavido viduḥ</incipit><explicit xml:lang="sa"><milestone facs="128" n="4r" unit="folio"/>
<lb n="6"/><gap reason="ellipsis"/>tiryyagyonisahasreṣu prāpya <pb n="4v" facs="129"/>teṣv api jāyate -
upakārāya yo brūyāt_ brāhmaṇārtthe gavām api |
brahmayoniśataṃ prāpya devatvam adhigacchati |
dharmmaśāstram idaṃ śakra mayā tava <lb n="2"/>vibhāṣitaṃ |
adhītya brāhmaṇo gacchet_ brahmaṇas sadmaśāśvataṃ |

ślokānān tu <unclear>caturṣṣaṣṭhīṃ</unclear> śrāvayed ya śṛṇoti ca | <del>pra</del> parvvasu prayato nityam ukta
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dānaphalaṃ labhet — <g ref="#pcl"/>
</explicit><finalRubric xml:lang="sa">brahaspatismṛtis samāptā - <g ref="#pcl"/></finalRubric></msItem></msContents>
